{title: 只要有你在我左右}
{title_pinyin: Zhǐ yào yǒu nǐ zài wǒ zuǒ yòu}
{key: C}
{tempo: 80}
{language: zh}

{start_of_verse: 主歌/Couplet}
只要有祢在我左右以   zhī yào yǒu mí zài wǒ zuǒ yòu yǐ
IfMyGodIswithMeS讚kean美ofSPra之lseP泉   IfMyGodIswithMeS zàn kean měi ofSPra zhī lseP quán
